snippet.title: SHARKSTORM - New Atari 2600 Game!
snippet.description:
Can your helicopter diffuse the deadly shark infested tornado?  Dodge the flying sharks to save humanity from weather most jawsome!!  My other games: http://theloon.itch.io/

* Each wave brings a unique Sharkstorm
* Tiger, Mako and Hammerhead among other flying adversaries
* 4k ROM without bankswitching, extra RAM or ARM assistance.
